## Dark Theme Support

The tabs tokens automatically support dark theme via CSS variables:

```css
[data-theme="dark"] .ui-Tabs,
.mds-tabs--on-dark {
  /* Dark theme tokens are automatically applied */
  /* No need to manually override if using --mds-tabs-* tokens */
}
```

## Why This Matters

1. **Design Consistency**: Tabs look the same across the entire application
2. **Theme Support**: Dark theme variants work automatically
3. **Maintainability**: Changes to tab styles happen in one place (tokens file)
4. **Future-Proofing**: When MDS updates, tabs update automatically
5. **Accessibility**: MDS tokens include proper contrast ratios and sizing

## Common Mistakes to Avoid

❌ **Don't**: Use color tokens directly
```css
color: #0070F3; /* Wrong */
color: var(--mds-color-electric-blue-500); /* Wrong */
```

✅ **Do**: Use tab-specific color tokens
```css
color: var(--mds-tabs-text-active); /* Correct */
```

❌ **Don't**: Use spacing tokens for tabs
```css
padding: var(--mds-spacing-md); /* Wrong */
gap: 8px; /* Wrong */
```

✅ **Do**: Use tab-specific spacing tokens
```css
padding: var(--mds-tabs-padding-y) var(--mds-tabs-padding-x); /* Correct */
gap: var(--mds-tabs-gap); /* Correct */
```

❌ **Don't**: Hard-code indicator dimensions
```css
border-bottom: 2px solid blue; /* Wrong */
```

✅ **Do**: Use tab indicator tokens
```css
border-bottom: var(--mds-tabs-indicator-height) solid var(--mds-tabs-indicator-color); /* Correct */
```

## Verification Checklist

When creating or reviewing tab components, ensure:

- [ ] All typography uses `--mds-tabs-font-*` tokens
- [ ] All colors use `--mds-tabs-text-*` or `--mds-tabs-background-*` tokens
- [ ] All spacing uses `--mds-tabs-padding-*` or `--mds-tabs-gap` tokens
- [ ] Indicator uses `--mds-tabs-indicator-*` tokens
- [ ] Transitions use `--mds-tabs-transition-*` tokens
- [ ] No hard-coded values for properties with available tokens
- [ ] No generic tokens where specific tab tokens exist
- [ ] Disabled state uses `--mds-tabs-text-disabled`
- [ ] Focus state uses `--mds-tabs-indicator-color` for outline

